clinical_particulars.therapeutic_indications: For the treatment of pulmonary artery anomalies

contraindications.pharmacodynamics: Tolazoline is a pulmonary vasodilator indicated used to decrease pulmonary vascular resistance PVR in persistent pulmonary hypertension of the newborn PPHN
